name: Magellan
description: Magellan by Oregon Cannabis Authority is a stimulating hybrid created for cannabis-forward creatives and explorers. This invigorating cross of OCA’s Cloud 9 and GG4 hits like a ton of bricks, putting a euphoric sizzle in the mind and a heavy-hitting buzz in the body. As the initial effects temper, the high becomes headier and uplifting, making this strain an excellent choice for social gatherings, brainstorming, and outdoor activity. When combined with these activities, Magellan can help alleviate depression and stress. Magellan also offers a unique aroma of fresh strawberries with a bright, piney undertone.

highlightedReviews.text: Truly fantastic new strain! Absolutely soaring, long lasting  physical and mental euphoria with this one. Diesely skunk on the inhale with a lingering pink fruit flavor. The product of many years of breeding, I expect this unique strain to stick around for a while.
Amazing hybrid!! Hits hard and makes me just the right amount of dopey stoned, but not messed up. Very happy, highly, and creative. Tingly and good for inflammation too.
